image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Mocha Cake: Our three layer vanilla sponge cake is combined with a Swiss mocha buttercream and is covered on the sides with crushed cashew nuts to bring you a great coffee flavor. If you don’t want the cashew nuts we are happy to cover the sides in chocolate shavings or nothing at all (7" or larger). Available daily in 9" round, 7" round, 4"x4" square, and a roll.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Loaves: We have smaller cakes available daily. Varieties include Jewish Apple, Cream Cheese Pound, and Pecan Chocolate Chip Pound Cake.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Devil's Food Cake: Three layers of moist dense devil’s food cake with chocolate buttercream. Available daily in 7" round.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Vanilla Cake: This cake is a three layer sponge cake and is filled with vanilla buttercream. White chocolate shavings cover the sides. Available daily in 7" round.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Chocolate Chip Pound Cake: Three layer chocolate pound cake layered with Swiss vanilla buttercream. Available daily in 7" round.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Blue Berry Pound Cake: Topped with icing, this could be a breakfast or a dessert.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Strawberry Pound Cake: Strawberry infused pound cake, covered in strawberry buttercream and topped with sliced strawberries. This is sold by the slice in the store (most days) or available as a whole cake by order.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Rum Cake: This cake is made with three layers of vanilla sponge cake, and is filled with a rum buttercream. The sides are covered in crushed cashew nuts. If you don’t want the cashew nuts we are happy to cover the sides in chocolate shavings or nothing at all (7" or larger). Available daily in 9" round, 7" round, and 4"x4" square.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Sacher Cake: This cake is three layers of velvety chocolate buttercream, spread over a moist Viennese chocolate sponge cake. The sides are covered in chocolate shavings. Available daily in 7" round.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Half & Half Cake: A layer of our vanilla sponge cake topped with a layer of light chocolate sponge cake. One half has vanilla buttercream, while the other half has chocolate buttercream. Available daily in 7" round.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: 7 Layer Cake: Seven layers of chocolate cake with our vanilla buttercream, compressed into a delicious cake. Available in one size only. Also available with chocolate buttercream and vanilla cake.

image:image.image:title: Signature Cakes
image:image.image:caption: Hazelnut Cake: This is our most popular cake. three layers of hazelnut sponge filled with vanilla buttercream. Our traditional chocolate shavings cover the sides. If you want to be fancy, order it with the mocha buttercream in lieu of the vanilla buttercream. Available daily in 9" round, 7" round, 4"x4" square, and a roll.

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Caramel Croquant: This delicious little 3 layer praline sponge cake is filled with caramel buttercream, finished with caramel, rolled in croquant.

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Strawberry Pound Cake: Strawberry infused pound cake, covered in strawberry buttercream and topped with sliced strawberries. This is sold by the slice in the store (most days) or available as a whole cake by order.

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Marjolaine: This wonderful pastry has four layers of crispy hazelnut meringue sandwiched with praline and chocolate buttercream, whipped cream, and covered in ganache. The Marjolaine can also be ordered in a cake form to feed 6 to 8 people. *Gluten Free, Kosher for Passover

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Brioche Bun with Pastry Cream Filling

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Almond Log: The Almond Log, a relative of the Almond Horseshoe, is a cross between a cookie and a pastry. It is chewy and crunchy with almond flavors rolled in toasted almond slivers. Then a strip of raspberry and apricot filling is added down the center. Goes great as a breakfast treat with coffee or tea. *Gluten Free

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Almond Horseshoe: The Almond Horseshoe is a cross between a cookie and a pastry. It is chewy and crunchy with almond flavors rolled in toasted almond slivers. Goes great as a breakfast treat with coffee or tea. *Gluten Free

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Peach and Pear Frangipane: This pastry starts with a butter tart dough crust, almond cake, with a hint of raspberry, almond slices, and topped off with peaches and pears. If you're an almond lover, this one is for you!

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Butterscotch Bow-tie: The Butterscotch Bowtie is one of the best products in the morning pastry category. Made with delicious pecans that are sprinkled with brown sugar, this truly is a treat. The pastry is a flaky layered pastry with buttery, sugary pecans baked in.

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Clichy: This is a seven layer coffee brushed biscuit, layered with coffee and chocolate buttercream, a hint of raspberry, covered in ganache. The clichy can also be ordered as a cake to feed 6 to 8 people.

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Chocolate Mozart: The Chocolate Mozart starts with a hazelnut meringue disk on the bottom, then a luscious layer of chocolate buttercream, chocolate cake, finished with white chocolate and a dollop of fresh whipped cream on top. This is a favorite of the bakers (and that's saying something).

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Napoleon: The Napoleon has three layers of flaky French pastry, layered with vanilla custard, fresh whipped cream, and a hint of raspberry. All of this deliciousness is enrobed in fondant. This pastry is as bold as the Emperor of France himself (though it wouldn't dare attempt a land-war in Asia).

image:image.image:title: Pastries
image:image.image:caption: Peanut Butter Candycake: Three layers of vanilla cake, peanut butter buttercream, covered in chocolate ganache, and coated with cake crumbs. If you love peanut butter cups, come try this on for size!

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Chinese Cookie: Shortbread cookie rolled with chocolate ganache in the center and chocolate sprinkles on the outside.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Hamantaschen: Our version on the traditional Jewish Purim cookie...available year round in apricot, cherry, prune, and poppy.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Chocolate Butter Cookie w/ Chocolate Drops

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Hazelnut Sandwich Cookie: Hazelnut cookies drizzled in white or regular chocolate, with either chocolate or raspberry in the center.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Butter Cookie Dipped in White Chocolate

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Starry Night: A chocolate cookie with white chocolate chips that (we think) looks just like a starry night.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Non-Pareils: Butter cookie covered in rainbow jimmies...a favorite of every kid!

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Bumble Bee Cookie: Peanut butter based cookie sweetened by honey, chock full of sunflower seeds and sesame seeds, and topped with a chocolate drizzle.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Signature Cookie: An invention of Donna's, this oatmeal cookie is packed full of walnuts and dried cranberries and topped with a flat icing.

image:image.image:title: Cookies
image:image.image:caption: Butter Cookie with White Chocolate Drop
